title: Lauryn & Michael Bosstick from The Skinny Confidential
description:
It’s a HUGE week for Lala! First, she’s celebrating 4 years of sobriety, and second, October 27th marks her self-proclaimed Independence Day! Lala shares how she celebrated both! She talks about her trip to the pumpkin patch with Ocean, and their fun day at Universal Studios with Scheana Shay and Summer Moon, and Brittany, Jax and Cruz! And Lauryn & Michael Bosstick from The Skinny Confidential join to talk parenting, mom guilt, reality TV, social media, and killing it in business!
